      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full length outdoor portrait of a man wearing a military uniform and a hat with a cockade. He is carrying a sword and holding a whip. He is standing in front of a wooden table on which field glasses and a canteen have been placed.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Hristo Petrunov (1859 - after 1937) was a cavalry officer during the Serbo-Bulgarian War of 1885, the Balkan Wars of 1912 - 1913, and the First World War. He became major general in 1900.</ab>
